OL,3,CWoman compensated by Ryanair following
OL,4,Cserious burns from spilt coffee
OL,6,FA woman from Hampshire who suffered
OL,7,Fserious burns from a cup of coffee on
OL,8,Fa Ryanair flight has been compensated
OL,9,Fby the airline.
OL,11,FDenise Elliott, from Southsea, was
OL,12,Fflying with friends to Majorca from
OL,13,FBournemouth, when she was handed a
OL,14,Fcoffee without a protective cup lid.
OL,16,FThe 63-year-old nurse was told the
OL,17,Fflight had run out of lids by the
OL,18,Fsteward who was serving customers from
OL,19,Fthe trolley.
