OL,3,CWoman compensated by Ryanair following
OL,4,Cserious burns from spilt coffee
OL,6,FDenise put the cup on her tray table,
OL,7,Fbut says it slid off, covering her
OL,8,Flegs in boiling hot coffee.
OL,10,FBecause of her occupation, Denise says
OL,11,Fshe immediately knew she needed to
OL,12,Ftreat her injuries with a cold-water
OL,13,Fcompress.
OL,15,F"I put my dress over my lap to help,
OL,16,Fbut I needed something absorbent
OL,17,Fcovered in cold water so I could douse
OL,18,Fthe temperature out of it (the
OL,19,Fburns)", Denise said.
