OL,3,CWoman compensated by Ryanair following
OL,4,Cserious burns from spilt coffee
OL,6,F"I asked them for a towel, or
OL,7,Fsomething like that, but they said
OL,8,Fthey didn't have anything on board
OL,9,Flike that so I had to do my own first
OL,10,Faid.
OL,12,F"When they did bring something, they
OL,13,Ffirst brought me some dry paper towels
OL,14,Fand I was lost for words.
OL,16,F"After that they came back with some
OL,17,Fwipes, but it turned out they were
OL,18,Fsurface wipes which, of course,
OL,19,Fcontain alcohol.
