OL,3,CWoman compensated by Ryanair following
OL,4,Cserious burns from spilt coffee
OL,6,F"Eventually, somebody came up with a
OL,7,Fbottle of burn gel. We asked to keep
OL,8,Fit for a second application, but the
OL,9,Fsteward said that wasn't possible and
OL,10,Fit had to go back into the first-aid
OL,11,Fkit.
OL,13,F"It was an absolute shocker."
OL,15,FFollowing the flight, Denise brought
OL,16,Fan injury claim against the airline
OL,17,Funder the Montreal Convention, which
OL,18,Fgoverns international air travel.
