OL,3,CWoman compensated by Ryanair following
OL,4,Cserious burns from spilt coffee
OL,6,FHer case was taken up by Hudgell
OL,7,FSolicitors, who put her concerns to
OL,8,Fthe airline, which denied all
OL,9,Fliabiility.
OL,11,FShortly before trial, Ryanair agreed
OL,12,Fto a #4,350 out of court settlement.
OL,14,FDenise said: "I didn't want to make a
OL,15,Ffuss, but what really got my goat was
OL,16,FRyanair's lack of urgency.
OL,18,F"It was never about money, but they
OL,19,Fdidn't listen and just kept batting my
OL,20,Fquestions away ` that's what made me
OL,21,Fpursue a claim."
