OL,3,CWoman compensated by Ryanair following
OL,4,Cserious burns from spilt coffee
OL,6,FDenise was represented by Tracy
OL,7,FStansfield, senior associate solicitor
OL,8,Ffor Hudgell Solicitor.
OL,10,FShe said: "It's always a daunting
OL,11,Fprospect, taking on a superpower like
OL,12,FRyanair, but the corporate giants of
OL,13,Fthis world are just as accountable for
OL,14,Ftheir actions as the rest of us.
OL,16,F"Denise believed in the truth, and we
OL,17,Fwere glad that she achieved a degree
OL,18,Fof closure for what happened on that
OL,19,Fflight, which is becoming an all-to-
OL,20,Ffamiliar story for holidaymakers.
