OL,3,CWoman compensated by Ryanair following
OL,4,Cserious burns from spilt coffee
OL,6,F"Over the last few years, we have
OL,7,Fnoticed a growing trend of
OL,8,Fholidaymakers suffering in-flight
OL,9,Fburns, often because of shoddily
OL,10,Fconstructed tray tables on planes.
OL,12,F"For the sake of their customers, this
OL,13,Fis something Ryanair and other
OL,14,Fairlines need to urgently fix."
OL,16,FRyanair have been contacted for a
OL,17,Fstatement.
